  "detailed_description": "<strong>Ride with The reaper </strong>is a challenging 2D <strong>action-driving game</strong>. Inspired by classics from the 8bit age.<br><br>The Reaper hunts drivers who do not have guts, everyone knows, so … what else?<br>You never lift your foot off the accelerator.<br>Avoid obstacles, jump sinkholes, drive impossible curves, dodge missiles, go through walls , and be faster than The Reaper driving like as if there was no tomorrow<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1058570/extras/a5387b8f0a67b20547449670051aeed4.avif?t=1557350911\" width=385 height=243 /></span> <br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Scrolling action driving game inspired by classics <br></li><li>Addictive gameplay<br></li><li>40 challenging levels<br></li><li>Big bosses<br></li><li>Items and power Ups<br></li><li>cool retro music<br></li><li>absurd humor</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1058570/extras/0925ed91e643879c7f191406f19f155a.poster.avif?t=1557350911\" width=640 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1058570/extras/0925ed91e643879c7f191406f19f155a.webm?t=1557350911\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1058570/extras/0925ed91e643879c7f191406f19f155a.mp4?t=1557350911\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
